DUBAI: US-Iraqi entrepreneur Huda Kattan’s brand, Huda Beauty, has been named as the biggest cosmetics label in 2021, according to a recent report by Cosmetify. For the latest updates, follow us on Instagram @arabnews.lifestyle The Cosmetify Index ranks the world’s biggest beauty brands based on search volume, increase in searches, Instagram followers, hashtags and engagement.  A post shared by Huda Kattan (@huda) This is the second time Kattan’s Dubai-based label has topped Cosmetify’s list. MAC Cosmetics ranks second, Anastasia Beverly Hills is third, Avon is fourth and The Body Shop is fifth. 